<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.7">
<l>aṉṟiṉ ṉātaṉa ceycicu pālaṉum,</l>
<l>niṉṟa nīṇmaru tummeru tumpuḷḷum</l>
<l>veṉṟi vēlviṟaṟ kañcaṉum vīḻamuṉ</l>
<l>koṉṟa vaṉvaril kūṭiṭu kūṭalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O circle! [You] be joined if</l>
<l rend="indent">He who in the past killed</l>
<l rend="indent">The evil-doing Śiśupāla,</l>
<l rend="indent">the tall Arjuna-trees that stood [in the way],</l>
<l rend="indent">bulls, a bird,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] the mighty Kaṃsa with a victory[-giving] spear</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [they] fell before [everyone]</l>
<l>comes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
